{
  "stem": "13817.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to, to close the business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what we did-- whatever we could to be sold to-- the stock was sold or given away or sold to a so-called-- to a friend of my grandpa who was-- he had the same business in a other city.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the house we were living in we had to evacuate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And like I said, before we moved to this Juden apartment in Cologne, and the Nazis made their headquarters in that house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The house wasn't owned by, by my mother, because when we were ready to buy a house the Nazis didn't allow it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when she was going to buy one, we had a lot of-- not a lot-- but we had quite some-- owned quite some agriculture land and pastures and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And our other house were the stables for the business of my uncles were in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was all owned by my mother at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But this is a different story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't think we should go into that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were living there, and then we were notified to-- we had to evac-- to evacuate the house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By then, it on the-- already the spring of '39.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't then want to live in that  little town anymore, because we didn't have any business.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We thought we would be better off to live in a big city where not everybody knows each other, and where, you know, wouldn't be too harassed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the German machinery of knowing everything and the Gestapo didn't make that much difference.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then all of a sudden, we had to wear the star.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So everybody-- there were too many people what knew you that you wouldn't wear the star, and would be afraid not to.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, when--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
